<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>meṉkācai māmalaraṉṉa meyyorkkum viriñcaṉukku
<lb n="2" break="no"/>m vaṉkācu tirttiṭum viccuvanātaṉ makiḻntirukkap
<lb n="3"/>poṉ kācai meyyeṉṟu teṭippakaikku mippūtala
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ttut teṉkāci <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> perumāḷ parākkiramat teṉṉavaṉe
<lb n="5" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> cakātta muṉṉūṟṟuṭaṉāyirat teṇpattañciṟ cīrāru mārkaḻi
<lb n="6"/><unclear>Ā</unclear>tiraināḷiṟ ciṟituṅkuṟṟam vārāta pūraṇaitaṉṉiṟ parākkirama māṟaṉe
<lb n="7" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> kayilāyantāṉ <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> kaṇṭaṉaṉe §
<lb n="8"/>kotaṟṟa pattiyaṟupattumuvartaṅ kūṭṭattilo tītaṟṟa veḷḷiccalam
<lb n="9" break="no"/>pakatto cempoṉampalatto vetattilo civalokattilo
<lb n="10"/>vicuvanātaṉirupātattilo ceṉṟu pukkāṉ parākkiramapāṇṭiyaṉe
</p>

